rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0001
rows.name:
My inn may be small, but I still
get customers.

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I get to hear plenty of stories from
travelers, too. It's one of life's little
pleasures...

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Never understood what the deal
with Acedia is though.

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Heard they're preaching the salvation
of a god on one hand, but also have
lots of scientists visiting the Holy See.

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0005
rows.name:
This mixture of religion and science...
It just doesn't sit right with me.

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Science is about using people's
ingenuity to explain the world, right?
But religion is in conflict with that.

rows.label: tlk70000067_03_msg0007
rows.name:
Just my opinion. Don't pay an
uneducated old guy like me no mind.
